#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
	int t;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--)
	{
		int r,j,sum=0,count=0,count1=0,max,min,i;
		cin>>min>>max;
		for(i=min;i<=max;i++)
		{
			sum=0;
			count1=0;
			j=i;
			while(j!=0)
			{
				r=j%10;
				sum=sum+r;
				j=j/10;
			}
			for(int k=1;k<=sum;k++)
			{
				if(sum%k==0)
				count1++;
			}
			if(count1==2)
			{
				count=count+1;
			}
		}
		cout<<count<<endl;
	}
}
